---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro"
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro"
---

<PageLayout
  title="About"
  description="Self-taught frontend engineer from Brazil. Building a life shaped by code, clarity, and intention."
>
  <article class="about container">
    <PageHeader title="About" subtitle="Self-taught. Brazilian. Building from the inside out." />

    <section class="about__body">
      <p>I came from outside the tech bubble.</p>

      <p>
        No Silicon Valley origin story. Just a secondhand MacBook, discipline, a lot of mistakes, and a quiet will to keep going.
      </p>

      <p>
        In 2018, I had the chance to visit Silicon Valley while helping at a tech event. That trip shifted how I saw technology, career, and what is possible.
      </p>

      <p>
        My career started in Brazil, but my vision has always been global. Today, I work remotely for a U.S. company based in New York, building a life shaped by code, clarity, and intention.
      </p>

      <p>
        This is my <strong>inner commit</strong>: to keep building a life that makes sense, from the inside out.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about__contact">
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Email <a
          id="contact-email"
          href="#"
          data-user="me"
          data-domain="ederchristian.com"
          aria-label="Email address (revealed on click)"
        ><span class="email-text">me <span class="email-sep">[at]</span> ederchristian <span class="email-sep">[dot]</span> com</span></a> or DM me on <a href="https://x.com/ederchristian" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <script>
      function wireEmail() {
        const link = document.getElementById("contact-email") as HTMLAnchorElement | null
        if (!link) return
        const user = link.dataset.user
        const domain = link.dataset.domain
        if (!user || !domain) return
        const address = `${user}@${domain}`
        link.setAttribute("href", `mailto:${address}`)
        const reveal = () => {
          const text = link.querySelector(".email-text")
          if (text) text.textContent = address
        }
        link.addEventListener("mouseenter", reveal, { once: true })
        link.addEventListener("focus", reveal, { once: true })
        link.addEventListener("click", reveal, { once: true })
      }
      wireEmail()
      document.addEventListener("astro:after-swap", wireEmail)
    </script>

    <footer class="about__foot">
      <p>I'm Brazilian and bilingual, but I write in English to reach the audience I'm building for.</p>
    </footer>
  </article>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: 64px;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .about__body p {
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: var(--lh-base);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }
  .about__body p:first-child {
    font-size: var(--fs-lede);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about__body strong {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about__contact {
    margin-top: 56px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .about__contact h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about__contact p {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: var(--lh-base);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .about__contact a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .email-sep {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }
  .about__foot {
    margin-top: 56px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: var(--fs-meta);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
